column2: SELECT TOP # s.SpecObjID,    s.z,    ph.u,   ph.g,   ph.r,   s.z,    L.ew,    L.sigma,    L.height,    dbo.fCosmoDl(s.z),    wave,    restWave,  FROM PhotoObjAll as ph,    SpecPhoto as s,   SpecLine  as L,   SpecObjAll as so    WHERE s.specClass = #      AND ph.specObjID = s.specObjID     AND L.specObjID = s.specObjID     AND so.specObjID = s.specObjID
